== 事件起因 ==

[[2002年巴厘島爆炸案|2002年巴厘島爆炸案]]，超過200人死亡。自此以後，印尼加強打擊[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]，而2003年，立法機關通過反恐法案<ref>{{cite book |editor= Ramraj, Hor, & Roach |title= Global Anti-Terrorism Law and Policy |url= https://archive.org/details/globalantiterror00ramr |year= 2005 |publisher= Cambridge University Press |isbn= 0521851254 |page= [https://archive.org/details/globalantiterror00ramr/page/295 295] }}</ref>。

巴厘島爆炸案肇事者回教祈禱團<ref>{{cite news |title=Bush condemns Bali bombings |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2002/US/10/13/Bush.bali/index.html |publisher=''CNN'' |date=2002-10-14 |accessdate=2009-07-18 |archive-date=2020-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106002916/http://edition.cnn.com/2002/US/10/13/Bush.bali/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是[[基地組織|基地組織]]相關連的團體，試圖在東南亞建立共同由回教國家統治的地方。<ref>{{cite book |editor= Biersteker T. J., & Eckert S. E. |title= Countering the Financing of Terrorism |year= 2007 |publisher= Routledge |isbn= 0415396433 |page= 63 }}</ref>

2009年的襲擊，剛在印尼總統選舉後9天。執法人員集中從回教祈禱團及其分支著手調查。<ref>{{cite news |title=Bombings, business and the future of Indonesia |url=http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-indonesia-bombs19-2009jul19,0,694548.story |publisher=''Los Angeles Times'' |date=2009-07-18 |accessdate=2009-07-18 |archive-date=2009-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090722063555/http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-indonesia-bombs19-2009jul19,0,694548.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>

